      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jose Maria Velasco</b>\n</p><p><b>Jose Maria Velasco</b>, (José Mº Velasco <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>)<br />\na Spanish computer chess aficionado, programmer, and author of the <a href=\"/Ippolit\" title=\"Ippolit\">Ippolit</a> open source <a href=\"/Category:Derivative\" title=\"Category:Derivative\">derivative</a> <a href=\"/Bouquet\" title=\"Bouquet\">Bouquet</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2011_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2011 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2013_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2013 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jose_Maria_Velasco&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2011_...\">2011 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jose_Maria_Velasco&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2011 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=399818&amp;t=38467\">Re: Visual C</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 19, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43714\">Bouquet New Chess Engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 15, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44110\">Bouquet 1.2 Relased</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 18, 2012</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2013_...\">2013 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jose_Maria_Velasco&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2013 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47400\">JukeBox_DEV1</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 03, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47418\">Evaluation values to drive the engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 05, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48481\">Windows 8.1 and Visual Studio 2013 preview</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 30, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49272\">LLVM toolchain on Windows</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 07, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49439\">Syzygy tablebases, work in Stockfish?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 23, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=537842&amp;highlight=#537842\">Re: LS-ratinglist (news &amp; comments)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 11, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51406\">Hakkapeliitta dev 63.7 by Mikko Aarnos</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 25, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Hakkapeliitta\" title=\"Hakkapeliitta\">Hakkapeliitta</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=564820\">GreKo 12.0 2002-2014 12 years development, Congrats!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">José Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 02, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/GreKo\" title=\"GreKo\">GreKo</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jose_Maria_Velasco&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67173\">LCZero in Fritz Gui and similar</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">José Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 20, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Leela Chess Zero</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jose_Maria_Velasco&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/chessbouquet/\">Chess Bouquet- JukeBox</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jose_Maria_Velasco&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ordinal_indicator#Galician.2C_Italian.2C_Portuguese.2C_and_Spanish\">The masculine ordinal indicator</a> U+00BA (º) is often confused with the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Degree_symbol\">degree sign</a> U+00B0 (°), which looks very similar in many fonts. Spanish uses the indicator letters in some abbreviations.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?t=44110&amp;start=2\">Re: Bouquet 1.2 Relased</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 19, 2012</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228203236\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 55/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 110/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6942-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228203236 and revision id 18360\n -->\n"
